CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - Allegheny All-Stars Defensive Starters -  Left to right, front line: Dennis Montani, Glassport; Charles Bursich, Etna; Bruce Brinklos, McKeesport; James Ribal, Penn Hills; Theodore Harris, Westinghouse; Ronald Cimino, Swissvale, and McLean, school unidentified. Backfield - William Vick, Braddock; Joseph Wyzkoski, North Catholic; John Vujevich, Clairton, and John Prislipsky, Wilkinsburg... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Allegheny County All-Star Jaycee football team members from left front row: Dennis Montani, Charles Bursich, Bruce Brinklos, James Ribal, Theodore Harris, Ronald Cimino, McLean; back: William Vick, Joseph Wyzkoski, John Vujevich, and John Prislipsky, posed on field
